## Best Practices

### DO ✅

```erb
<!-- Use asset helpers -->
<%= image_tag "logo.png" %>
<%= stylesheet_link_tag "application" %>

<!-- Optimize images before adding -->
<!-- Use WebP for modern browsers -->
<picture>
  <source srcset="<%= asset_path('hero.webp') %>" type="image/webp">
  <%= image_tag "hero.jpg", alt: "Hero" %>
</picture>

<!-- Lazy load images below the fold -->
<%= image_tag "image.jpg", loading: "lazy" %>

<!-- Organize assets logically -->
app/assets/images/icons/check.svg
app/assets/images/illustrations/empty-state.svg

<!-- Use descriptive filenames -->
hero-background.jpg  # Good
img1.jpg            # Bad
```

### DON'T ❌

```erb
<!-- Don't hardcode asset paths -->
<img src="/assets/logo.png">  <!-- Bad! -->
<%= image_tag "logo.png" %>   <!-- Good! -->

<!-- Don't put assets in public/ (unless static) -->
public/logo.png              <!-- Bad -->
app/assets/images/logo.png   <!-- Good -->

<!-- Don't use huge unoptimized images -->
<!-- Optimize and resize before adding -->

<!-- Don't forget alt text -->
<%= image_tag "logo.png" %>  <!-- Bad -->
<%= image_tag "logo.png", alt: "Company Logo" %>  <!-- Good -->

<!-- Don't use data URIs for large images -->
<!-- Use actual files with asset pipeline -->
```

