## Troubleshooting

### Assets Not Loading in Production

```bash
# Ensure assets are precompiled
rails assets:precompile

# Check public/assets/ directory exists
ls public/assets/

# Verify asset_host is correct
rails runner "puts Rails.application.config.asset_host"

# Check web server serves static files
# Nginx: ensure static files are served
# Kamal: ensure volumes are mounted correctly
```

### Missing Images in Development

```bash
# Restart Rails server
rails server

# Check file exists
ls app/assets/images/logo.png

# Check file permissions
chmod 644 app/assets/images/logo.png
```

